A frustrated person sitting cross-legged on a living room floor surrounded by tangled ethernet cables and a blinking router, their hair slightly disheveled, bathed in the harsh blue glow of multiple device indicator lights in an otherwise dark room. The scene is rendered in a Studio Ghibli style with soft, expressive character design and warm ambient shadows contrasting with the cold technological light. Small dust particles float in the air, and through a window, a peaceful Singapore skyline at dusk is visible, emphasizing the contrast between the serene outside world and the indoor tech chaos. The router sits prominently on a low table, its lights blinking erratically like an uncooperative creature.
